      • toString

        String toString()
        Returns a string representation of this CharFloatMap. The string representation consists of a list of the map's key-value pairs in the order they are returned by its iterator. The key and value in each key-value pair are separated by a colon (":") and each pair is enclosed in square brackets ("[]"). Adjacent key-value pairs are separated by the characters ", " (comma and space). Keys and values are converted to strings as by String#valueOf().
